  • org.kathrynhuxtable.maven.plugins:imagegenerator-maven-plugin:maven-plugin:1.2-SNAPSHOT

    Image Generator Maven plugin

    Description: A Maven plugin to generate image files from an XML description of objects. This allows for constructor arguments and client properties, and is useful for creating documentation for Swing look and feel packages, and also for documenting custom components.

    URL: http://khuxtable.github.com/imagegenerator-maven-plugin

    Project License: The Apache Software License, Version 2.0

Maven can be extended by plugins to utilise a number of other development tools for reporting or the build process.
